# TradeLog — Project Rules & Documentation

## 1. Database Schema (Firestore)

### Collection: `users/{uid}`
| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| uid | string | Firebase Auth UID |
| email | string | User email |
| displayName | string | Display name |
| role | string | `mentor` / `collaborator` / `client` |
| createdAt | string | ISO timestamp |

### Collection: `trades/{id}`
| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| uid | string | Owner UID |
| ticker | string | Stock symbol (uppercase) |
| entryPrice | number | Entry price |
| exitPrice | number \| null | Exit price (null if open) |
| date | string | Trade date (YYYY-MM-DD) |
| notes | string | Trade rationale / notes |
| chartUrl | string | Firebase Storage URL for chart screenshot |
| status | string | `open` / `closed` |
| createdAt | string | ISO timestamp |

### Collection: `clients/{id}`
| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| uid | string | Mentor UID |
| name | string | Client/mentee name |
| riskProfile | string | `conservative` / `moderate` / `aggressive` |
| type | string | `individual` / `group` |
| members | string[] | Group member names |
| notes | string | Background notes |
| createdAt | string | ISO timestamp |

### Collection: `insights/{id}`
| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| clientId | string | Reference to client doc |
| uid | string | Mentor UID |
| ticker | string | Stock symbol |
| advice | string | Trade advice given |
| riskLevel | string | `low` / `medium` / `high` |
| outcome | string | `pending` / `profit` / `loss` / `neutral` |
| outcomeNotes | string | What happened |
| createdAt | string | ISO timestamp |

---

## 2. Color Palettes

### Dark Mode
| Token | Hex | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| bg-primary | `#0D1117` | Main background |
| bg-secondary | `#161B22` | Cards, sidebar |
| bg-tertiary | `#1C2129` | Nested surfaces |
| bg-hover | `#21262D` | Interactive hover |
| text-primary | `#E6EDF3` | Main text |
| text-secondary | `#8B949E` | Secondary text |
| text-muted | `#6E7681` | Muted/hint text |
| accent | `#58A6FF` | Links, active state |
| accent-hover | `#79C0FF` | Accent hover |
| success | `#3FB950` | Profit / positive |
| danger | `#F85149` | Loss / negative |
| warning | `#D29922` | Caution |
| border | `#30363D` | Borders |

### Light Mode
| Token | Hex | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| bg-primary | `#F6F8FA` | Main background |
| bg-secondary | `#FFFFFF` | Cards, sidebar |
| bg-tertiary | `#EEF1F5` | Nested surfaces |
| bg-hover | `#E8ECF0` | Interactive hover |
| text-primary | `#1F2328` | Main text |
| text-secondary | `#656D76` | Secondary text |
| text-muted | `#8B949E` | Muted/hint text |
| accent | `#0969DA` | Links, active state |
| accent-hover | `#0550AE` | Accent hover |
| success | `#1A7F37` | Profit / positive |
| danger | `#CF222E` | Loss / negative |
| warning | `#9A6700` | Caution |
| border | `#D0D7DE` | Borders |

